description:
&lt;p&gt;Theatre Admissions Unit is a busy and dynamic unit. We admit all elective theatre patients as well as admitting and discharging all emergency day cases.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Unit is currently open Monday to Friday from 7:00am – 8.30pm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and motivated staff nurse to join our small friendly team. We have an opportunity for a proactive, forward thinking person to join us, who will make a positive contribution to patient care and their experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good communication skills are essential and experience of working on a surgical ward would be desirable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The area will provide a comprehensive induction and orientation programme. To support you, the unit has a practice development nurse and established competencies for you to work towards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are proud to be able to offer a variety of flexible working options and contracts. For further information please refer to the Flexible Working for Registered Nurses document which is attached to this advert.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Claire Aldridge&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Team Leader&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address claire.aldridge2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 01273 696955 x 7444&lt;/p&gt;
